extendedData.name: OracleText
extendedData.value:
The 2022 Starter Kit is ideal for any pair of new Magic players that walk through your doors, as they give newcomers the opportunity to dive into their first game in-person and continue the fun online with redeemable Magic: The Gathering Arena code cards.

Starter Kits are being refreshed for 2022 and will collect cards from Innistrad: Midnight Hunt, Innistrad: Crimson Vow, Kamigawa: Neon Dynasty, and Streets of New Capenna.

Contents:
• two (2) sixty-card decks (including 2 outward facing foils)
• two (2) Reference cards
• one (1) Arena variable code card
• one (1) Arena insert
• one (1) Rules & World of Magic booklet
• two (2) Tuck boxes for decks
• one (1) Foil Set Up box

Magic: The Gathering Streets of New Capenna Bundle | 8 Set Boosters + Accessories
KEY PRODUCT FEATURES

DESCRIPTION
The Streets of New Capenna Bundle contains 8 Streets of New Capenna Set Boosters—the best boosters to open just for fun—plus exclusive accessories, with 40 basic lands (20 traditional foils and 20 nonfoils), 1 traditional foil promo card with Bundle-exclusive alternate art, 1 oversized Spindown life counter, 1 card storage box, and 2 reference cards.

extendedData.name: OracleText
extendedData.value:
Collect one of each the 5 designs of Theme Boosters for Streets of New Capenna.

The Streets of New Capenna Theme Booster contains 5 Streets of New Capenna Theme Boosters, with 1 for each crime family: The Obscura (White-Blue-Black), The Maestros (Blue-Black-Red), The Riveteers (Black-Red-Green), The Cabaretti (Red-Green-White), and The Brokers (Green-White-Blue).

Each booster contains 35 cards, with a combination of 1–2 card(s) of rarity Rare or higher (2 in 10% of packs) and 33–34 Uncommon and Common SNC cards. A showcase card can be found in 30% of packs.

Gifted magicians, elite assassins, party monsters, destruction workers, and demonic lawyers—join one of New Capenna’s powerful families and scheme your way to riches with a theme booster that gives you the types of cards you want.
